WEBVTT

00:06.707 --> 00:12.921
What the world needs now is love, sweet love.

00:14.008 --> 00:19.700
It's the only thing that there's just too little of.

00:20.017 --> 00:26.843
What the world needs now is love, sweet love.

00:27.453 --> 00:33.091
No, not just for some but for everyone.

00:34.045 --> 00:38.830
Lord, we don't need another mountain.

00:39.630 --> 00:45.171
There are mountains and hillsides enough to climb.

00:45.685 --> 00:49.530
There are oceans and rivers...

00:49.881 --> 00:51.164
...enough to cross,...

00:51.597 --> 00:52.976
...enough to last...

00:53.046 --> 00:57.115
...enough to last 'til the end of time.

00:57.190 --> 01:03.965
What the world needs now is love, sweet love.

01:04.763 --> 01:10.233
It's the only thing that there's just too little of.

01:10.813 --> 01:17.283
What the world needs now is love, sweet love.

01:17.893 --> 01:23.934
No, not just for some but for everyone.

